|             |            | (SW->HW)   |               |         |        |          | Bitwidth  | Burst Length | Burst Length | Outstanding | Outstanding |                   |
+-------------+------------+------------+---------------+---------+--------+----------+-----------+--------------+--------------+-------------+-------------+-------------------+
| m_axi_gmem0 | READ_ONLY  | 64 -> 64   | 64            | 0       | slave  | 0        | 0         | 16           | 16           | 16          | 16          | BRAM=4            |
| m_axi_gmem1 | READ_ONLY  | 32 -> 32   | 64            | 0       | slave  | 0        | 0         | 16           | 16           | 16          | 16          | BRAM=2            |
| m_axi_gmem2 | READ_ONLY  | 32 -> 32   | 64            | 0       | slave  | 0        | 0         | 16           | 16           | 16          | 16          |                   |
| m_axi_gmem3 | WRITE_ONLY | 32 -> 32   | 64            | 0       | slave  | 0        | 0         | 16           | 16           | 16          | 16          | BRAM=2            |
| m_axi_gmem4 | READ_ONLY  | 8 -> 8     | 64            | 0       | slave  | 0        | 0         | 16           | 16           | 16          | 16          | BRAM=2            |
| m_axi_gmem5 | READ_ONLY  | 512 -> 512 | 64            | 0       | slave  | 0        | 512       | 16           | 16           | 16          | 16          | BRAM=29           |
| m_axi_gmem6 | READ_ONLY  | 512 -> 512 | 64            | 0       | slave  | 0        | 512       | 16           | 16           | 16          | 16          | BRAM=29           |
+-------------+------------+------------+---------------+---------+--------+----------+-----------+--------------+--------------+-------------+-------------+-------------------+

* S_AXILITE Interfaces
+---------------+------------+---------------+--------+----------+
| Interface     | Data Width | Address Width | Offset | Register |
+---------------+------------+---------------+--------+----------+
| s_axi_control | 32         | 8             | 16     | 0        |
+---------------+------------+---------------+--------+----------+

* S_AXILITE Registers
+---------------+-------------------------+--------+-------+--------+--------------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Interface     | Register                | Offset | Width | Access | Description                          | Bit Fields                                                           |
+---------------+-------------------------+--------+-------+--------+--------------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| s_axi_control | CTRL                    | 0x00   | 32    | RW     | Control signals                      | 0=AP_START 1=AP_DONE 2=AP_IDLE 3=AP_READY 7=AUTO_RESTART 9=INTERRUPT |
